<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>

<head>
    <meta charset="utf-8">
    <title>Payment Successful</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            line-height: 1.6;
            color: #333;
        }

        .container {
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            padding: 20px;
        }

        .header {
            background-color: #4CAF50;
            color: white;
            padding: 20px;
            text-align: center;
        }

        .content {
            padding: 20px;
            background-color: #f9f9f9;
        }

        .footer {
            text-align: center;
            padding: 20px;
            font-size: 12px;
            color: #666;
        }

        .details {
            background-color: white;
            padding: 15px;
            border-radius: 5px;
            margin: 20px 0;
        }

        .details table {
            width: 100%;
        }

        .details td {
            padding: 8px;
        }

        .label {
            font-weight: bold;
        }
    </style>
</head>

<body>
    <div class="container">
        <div class="header">
            <h1>Payment Successful!</h1>
        </div>
        <div class="content">
            <p>Dear {{name}},</p>
            <p>Thank you for your payment. Your subscription has been successfully activated.</p>

            <div class="details">
                <h3>Transaction Details</h3>
                <table>
                    <tr>
                        <td class="label">Plan:</td>
                        <td>{{planName}}</td>
                    </tr>
                    <tr>
                        <td class="label">Amount:</td>
                        <td>{{amount}} {{currency}}</td>
                    </tr>
                    <tr>
                        <td class="label">Transaction ID:</td>
                        <td>{{transactionId}}</td>
                    </tr>
                    <tr>
                        <td class="label">Date:</td>
                        <td>{{paymentDate}}</td>
                    </tr>
                </table>
            </div>

            <p>You can now enjoy all the premium features included in your plan.</p>
            <p>If you have any questions, please contact our support team.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="footer">
            <p>&copy; {{currentYear}} SfinX Platform. All rights reserved.</p>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>

</html>